14\u7b26\u5408\u4eba\u6743\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\u8fc7\u6e21\u5230\u96f6\u78b3\u7ecf\u6d4e\u548c\u6784\u5efa\u66f4\u6709\u6d3b\u529b\u7684\u793e\u4f1a\u3002<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\">\u9605\u8bfb\u66f4\u591a<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"grid grid-5 post-list\"><article class=\"grid-item aimc-ignore\" aria-label=\"Article: 2019\u5e74\u5ea6\u4eba\u6743\u62a5\u544a\" style=\"aiic:ignore;background-image: url('https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/266870-scaled-1-scaled.jpg')\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"grid-content\"><span class=\"grid-itemMeta\"><\/span><h3 class=\"grid-itemTitle\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/2019-annual-report\/\" tabindex=\"0\">2019\u5e74\u5ea6\u4eba\u6743\u62a5\u544a<\/a><\/h3><\/div><\/article><article class=\"grid-item aimc-ignore\" aria-label=\"Article: 2020\u5e74\u5ea6\u4eba\u6743\u62a5\u544a\uff1a\u8bb0\u5f55\u5168\u7403149\u4e2a\u56fd\u5bb6\u4eba\u6743\u72b6\u51b5\" style=\"aiic:ignore;background-image: url('https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/275280-640x400.jpg')\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"grid-content\"><span class=\"grid-itemMeta\"><\/span><h3 class=\"grid-itemTitle\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/2020-annual-report\/\" tabindex=\"0\">2020\u5e74\u5ea6\u4eba\u6743\u62a5\u544a\uff1a\u8bb0\u5f55\u5168\u7403149\u4e2a\u56fd\u5bb6\u4eba\u6743\u72b6\u51b5<\/a><\/h3><\/div><\/article><article class=\"grid-item aimc-ignore\" aria-label=\"Article: 2020\u5e74\u5ea6\u4e2d\u56fd\u4eba\u6743\u62a5\u544a\" style=\"aiic:ignore;background-image: url('https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/275286-640x400.jpg')\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"grid-content\"><span class=\"grid-itemMeta\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/category\/region-country\/asia-and-the-pacific\/china\/\" tabindex=\"0\">\u4e2d\u56fd<\/a><\/span><h3 class=\"grid-itemTitle\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/r